trans-unit.source: Represents the result of an <see cref="T:System.Data.Objects.ObjectQuery`1" /> as an enumerable collection of objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa o resultado de uma <see cref="T:System.Data.Objects.ObjectQuery`1" /> como uma coleção enumerável de objetos.

trans-unit.source: This class implements <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> and <xref:System.IDisposable>.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe implementa <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> e <xref:System.IDisposable>.

trans-unit.source: Instances of this class are returned from the <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectQuery%601.Execute%2A> method and from the <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectQuery%601.System%23Collections%23Generic%23IEnumerable%7BT%7D%23GetEnumerator%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.
trans-unit.target: As instâncias dessa classe são retornadas do <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectQuery%601.Execute%2A> método e o <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectQuery%601.System%23Collections%23Generic%23IEnumerable%7BT%7D%23GetEnumerator%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> método.

trans-unit.source: An enumerator that iterates through the query results.
trans-unit.target: Um enumerador que itera pelos resultados da consulta.

trans-unit.source: The enumerator must be disposed when no longer needed.
trans-unit.target: O enumerador deve ser descartado quando forem mais necessários.

trans-unit.source: Using the `foreach` statement (`For Each` in Visual Basic) ensures that the enumerator is correctly disposed when iteration over the results is complete.
trans-unit.target: Usando o `foreach` instrução (`For Each` no Visual Basic) garante que o enumerador corretamente é descartado quando a iteração sobre os resultados for concluída.
